DIVERSIONS

column2:
FAA confirms:

“Due to WEATHER / THUNDERSTORMS, there is a Traffic Management (Ground Stop) Program in effect for traffic arriving LGA.”

FWIW, most of the major east coast airports are also experiencing weather delays.

F-15s were scrambled and it now appears the plane has crashed. No confirmation whether it was shot down. https://t.co/TDyoLkkLO0
